data.title: Remember this timeless movie?[small][i]”Stand Up and Cheer,” 1934[/i][small]
data.meta_description: On April 20th, 1934, Shirley Temple's movie debut, “Stand Up and Cheer,” premiered in New York City. To see the entire photo collection of Shirley Temple through the decades, visit http://memlan.es/TempleCollection.
